BLAKE3 C implementation
=======================

Vendored from the official BLAKE3 reference repository:

    https://github.com/BLAKE3-team/BLAKE3
    Version: 1.8.5 (from the c/ directory)

BLAKE3 was designed by Jack O'Connor, Jean-Philippe Aumasson, Samuel
Neves, and Zooko Wilcox-O'Hearn.

