Vendored files
--------------

Compiled in this package:

  blake3.h, blake3.c, blake3_dispatch.c, blake3_portable.c,
  blake3_impl.h  (all targets)
  blake3_neon.c  (arm64 only)

Vendored but not yet compiled (x86-64 SIMD kernels, kept for a future
release that enables them):

  blake3_sse2.c, blake3_sse41.c, blake3_avx2.c, blake3_avx512.c

The x86-64 assembly variants and the multithreading (TBB) sources from
upstream are not vendored; they are not used by this package.

No source files were modified. The wrapper that calls into this code lives
in src/blake3_shim.c and lib/ in the parent package and is MIT licensed.
